    {
      "time_start": 13.5,
      "duration": 1.0,
      "action": "create",
      "target_element_id": "vertex_new",
      "params": {}
    },
    {
      "time_start": 14.5,
      "duration": 1.5,
      "action": "write",
      "target_element_id": "vertex_label_new",
      "params": {}
    },
    {
      "time_start": 16.0,
      "duration": 1.5,
      "action": "write",
      "target_element_id": "title_text",
      "params": {}
    },
    {
      "time_start": 17.5,
      "duration": 6.0,
      "action": "create",
      "target_element_id": "equation_summary",
      "params": {}
    },
    {
      "time_start": 23.5,
      "duration": 1.0,
      "action": "indicate",
      "target_element_id": "transformed_curve",
      "params": {
        "indicate_type": "circumscribe"
      }
    }
  ],
  "narration": "同学们，今天我们来学习二次函数的图像变换。首先，我们在坐标系中画出最基本的二次函数 y 等于 x 平方的图像，它是一条蓝色的抛物线，顶点在原点 (0, 0)。现在，我们来看变换过程。先将抛物线向右平移 2 个单位，再向上平移 1 个单位。可以看到，红色的新抛物线 y 等于 (x 减 2) 的平方加 1，顶点从 (0, 0) 移动到了 (2, 1)。总结一下变换规律：在函数表达式中，x 减 h 表示向右平移 h 个单位，加 k 表示向上平移 k 个单位。",
  "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural"
}
